            "title": "日股半日低收42點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">東京股市偏軟。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">日經指數先高後低，半日收報38445點，跌42點，跌幅0.11%。</p>\n</div>",
